http://www.skis.com/Volkl-One-W-Womens-Skis-2015/362657P,default,pd.html

The Volkl One W is a perfect pow ski for the ladies that are looking in the ultimate in float and smearability in the deep stuff. Volkl's new Tapered Shape prevents your tips and tails from getting caught up in the snow. The Full Rocker Profile will keep you surfing on top of the snow, and the rocker in the tail will smear turns beautifully when its waist deep. If you are always searching for the one, here it is with the new Volkl One W.
